erife]]\n| \n|-\n| 1964\n| M\u00aa Jos\u00e9 Ulla\n| [[Madrid (province)|Madrid]]\n| \n|-\n| 1965\n| Alicia Borr\u00e1s\n| [[Barcelona (province)|Barcelona]]\n| \n|-\n|-style=\"background-color:GOLD; font-weight: bold\"\n| 1966\n| Paquita Torres P\u00e9rez\n| [[M\u00e1laga (province)|M\u00e1laga]]\n| [[Miss Europe|Miss Europe 1967]]\n|-\n| 1967\n| Paquita Delgado S\u00e1nchez\n| [[Province of C\u00f3rdoba (Spain)|C\u00f3rdoba]]\n| \n|-\n| 1968\n| Amparo Rodrigo\n| [[Valencia (province)|Valencia]]\n| \n|-\n|-style=\"background-color:GOLD; font-weight: bold\"\n| 1969\n| Noelia Afonso\n| [[Tenerife (province)|Tenerife]]\n| [[Miss Europe|Miss Europe 1970]]\n|-\n| 1970\n| Josefina Rom\u00e1n\n| [[C\u00e1diz (province)|C\u00e1diz]]\n| \n|-\n| 1971\n| Maria del Carmen Mu\u00f1oz\n| [[Madrid (province)|Madrid]]\n| \n|-\n| 1972\n| Roc\u00edo Mart\u00edn Madrigal\n| [[Province of Seville|Sevilla]]\n| \n|-\n|-style=\"background-color:GOLD; font-weight: bold\"\n| [[Miss Universe 1973|1973]]\n| [[Amparo Mu\u00f1oz]]\n| [[M\u00e1laga (province)|M\u00e1laga]]\n| [[Miss Universe 1974]]\n|-\n| 1974\n| Nelly Rodriguez\n| [[Tenerife (province)|Tenerife]]\n| \n|-\n| 1975\n| Olga Fern\u00e1ndez P\u00e9rez\n| [[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n| \n|-\n| 1976\n| Luz Mar\u00eda Polegre Hern\u00e1ndez\n| [[Tenerife (province)|Tenerife]]\n| \n|-\n| 1977\n| Guillermina Ruiz Dom\u00e9nech\n| [[Balearic Islands|Islas Baleares]]\n| \n|-\n| 1978\n| Gloria Mar\u00eda Valenciano\n| [[Las Palmas (province)|Las Palmas]]\n| \n|-\n| 1979\n| [[Mar\u00eda Dolores Forner|Mar\u00eda Dolores Forner Toro]]\n| [[Madrid (province)|Madrid]]\n| \n|-\n| 1980\n| [[Frances Ondiviela|Francisca Ondiviela]]\n| [[Las Palmas (province)|Las Palmas]]\n| \n|-\n| 1981\n| Cristina P\u00e9rez Cottrell\n| [[M\u00e1laga (province)|M\u00e1laga]]\n| \n|-\n| 1982\n| Ana Isabel Herrero Garc\u00eda\n| [[Teruel (province)|Teruel]]\n| \n|-\n| 1983\n| [[Garbi\u00f1e Abasolo|Garbi\u00f1e Abasolo Garc\u00eda]]\n| [[Biscay|Vizcaya]]\n|