z|Eva Mar\u00eda Gonz\u00e1lez Fern\u00e1ndez]]\n| [[Province of Seville|Sevilla]]\n|   \n|-\n| [[Miss Spain 2004|2004]]\n| [[Mar\u00eda Jes\u00fas Ruiz Garz\u00f3n]] <ref name=\"seattlepi.com 2004\">{{cite web | title=Miss Universe (2004) -- National Costumes | website=seattlepi.com | date=May 26, 2004 | url=http://www.seattlepi.com/news/slideshow/Miss-Universe-2004-National-Costumes-7431.php | accessdate=April 1, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=Miss Spain 2004. Maria Jesus Garzon, Miss Jaen ... | website=Getty Images | date=March 28, 2004 | url=http://www.gettyimages.in/detail/news-photo/miss-spain-2004-maria-jesus-garzon-miss-jaen-has-been-news-photo/93063210 | accessdate=April 1, 2016}}</ref>\n| [[Province of Ja\u00e9n (Spain)|Ja\u00e9n]]\n|  \n|-\n| 2005\n| Ver\u00f3nica Hidalgo\n| [[Gerona (province)|Gerona]]\n|  \n|-\n| 2006\n| [[Elisabeth Reyes|Elisabeth Reyes Villegas]]\n| [[M\u00e1laga (province)|M\u00e1laga]]\n|  \n|-\n| 2007\n| Natalia Zabala Arroyo\n| [[Guip\u00fazcoa]]\n|  \n|-\n| [[Miss Spain 2008|2008]]\n| [[Patricia Yurena Rodr\u00edguez]]<ref name=\"canarias7\"/>\n| [[Tenerife (province)|Tenerife]]\n| \n|-\n| [[Miss Spain 2009|2009]]\n| [[Est\u00edbaliz Pereira|Est\u00edbaliz Pereira R\u00e1bade]]\n| [[A Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n| \n|-\n| [[Miss Spain 2010|2010]]\n| [[Paula Guill\u00f3|Paula Guill\u00f3 Sempere]]<ref name=\"hola\"/>\n| [[Province of Teruel|Teruel]]\n| \n|-\n| [[Miss Spain 2011|2011]]\n| [[Andrea Huisgen]]\n| [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]]\n| {{n/a|Last Miss Espa\u00f1a who sent at the Miss Universe pageant and last edition of Miss Espa\u00f1a}}\n|- \n|}\n\n===2013-present===\n{| class=\"sortable\" border=\"5\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #FFFFFF; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%; text-align:center\"\n|- \n!width=\"60\"|Year||width=\"300\"|Miss Universo Espa\u00f1a & Miss Mundo Espa\u00f1a<br>(Miss Universe Spain & Miss World 