igas Mederos \n| Unplaced\n| \n|-\n| 1987\n| [[M\u00e1laga (province)|M\u00e1laga]]\n| Remedios Cervantes Montoya \n| Unplaced\n| \n|-\n| 1986\n| [[M\u00e1laga (province)|M\u00e1laga]]\n| Isabel Tur Espinosa \n| Unplaced\n| \n|-\n|-style=\"background-color:#FFFF66;\"\n| 1985\n| [[Province of Seville|Seville]]\n| [[Teresa S\u00e1nchez L\u00f3pez|Maria Teresa S\u00e1nchez L\u00f3pez]] \n| '''1st Runner-up'''\n|\n|-\n|-style=\"background-color:#FADADD;\"\n| 1984\n| [[Biscay|Vizcaya]]\n| [[Garbi\u00f1e Abasolo|Garbi\u00f1e Abasolo Garc\u00eda]]\n| Unplaced\n| '''Miss Photogenic'''\n|-\n|-style=\"background-color:#FFFF99;\"\n| 1983\n| [[Teruel (province)|Teruel]]\n| Ana Isabel Herrero Garc\u00eda\n| '''Top 12'''\n| \n|-\n| 1982\n| [[M\u00e1laga (province)|M\u00e1laga]]\n| Cristina P\u00e9rez Cottrell \n| Unplaced\n| \n|-\n| 1981\n| [[Las Palmas (province)|Las Palmas]]\n| [[Frances Ondiviela|Francisca Ondiviela]] \n| Unplaced\n| \n|-\n| 1980\n| [[Asturias]]\n| Yolanda Mar\u00eda Hoyos Vega\n| Unplaced\n| \n|-\n| 1979\n| [[Las Palmas (province)|Las Palmas]]\n| Gloria Mar\u00eda Valenciano \n| Unplaced\n| \n|-\n|-style=\"background-color:#FFFF66;\"\n| 1978\n| [[Balearic Islands|Islas Baleares]]\n| Guillermina Ruiz Dom\u00e9nech\n| '''2nd Runner-up'''\n|  \n|-\n|-style=\"background-color:#FFFF99;\"\n| 1977\n| [[Tenerife (province)|Tenerife]]\n| Luz Mar\u00eda Polegre Hern\u00e1ndez \n| '''Top 12''' \n|  \n|-\n| 1976\n| [[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n| Olga Fern\u00e1ndez P\u00e9rez\n| Unplaced\n| \n|-\n| 1975\n| [[Tenerife (province)|Tenerife]]\n| Consuelo Mart\u00edn L\u00f3pez \n| Unplaced\n| \n|-\n|-style=\"background-color:GOLD; font-weight: bold\"\n| 1974\n| [[M\u00e1laga (province)|M\u00e1laga]]\n| [[Amparo Mu\u00f1oz|Amparo Mu\u00f1oz Quesada]] \n| [[Miss Universe 1974]]\n| \n|-\n|-style=\"background-color:#FFFF66;\"\n| 1973\n| [[Province of Seville|Seville]]\n| Roc\u00edo Mart\u00edn Madrigal \n| '''3rd Runner-up'''\n| '''Best National Costume'''\n|-\n| 1972\n