{"title_page": "Daniel Bernard (footballer)", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{short description|French footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name           = Daniel Bernard\n|image          = \n|image_size     = \n|caption        = \n|fullname       = \n|birth_date     = {{birth date|1949|9|29|df=y}}\n|birth_place    = [[Paris]], France\n|death_date     = {{death date and age|2020|4|9|1949|9|29|df=y}}\n|death_place    = \n|height         = 1.77m<ref name=\"auto\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.footballdatabase.eu/fr/joueur/details/45852|title=Daniel Bernard - Stats - palmar\u00e8s|website=www.footballdatabase.eu}}</ref>\n|position       = [[Goalkeeper (association football)|Goalkeeper]]\n|youthyears1    = \n|youthclubs1    = \n|years1         = 1968\u20131969\n|clubs1         = [[Paris-Neuilly]]\n|caps1          = 25\n|goals1         = 0\n|years2         = 1969\u20131977\n|clubs2         = [[Stade Rennais F.C.|Rennes]]\n|caps2          = 152\n|goals2         = 0\n|years3         = 1977\u20131978\n|clubs3         = [[Paris Saint-Germain F.C.|Paris Saint-Germain]]\n|caps3          = 29\n|goals3         = 0\n|years4         = 1978\u20131984\n|clubs4         = [[Stade Brestois 29|Brest]]\n|caps4          = 188\n|goals4         = 0\n|years5         = 1984\u20131985\n|clubs5         = [[AS Monaco FC|Monaco]]\n|caps5          = 13\n|goals5         = 0\n|totalcaps      = 407\n|totalgoals     = 0\n|nationalyears1 = \n|nationalteam1  = France youth\n|nationalcaps1  = \n|nationalgoals1 = \n}}\n'''Daniel Bernard''' (29 September 1949 \u2013 9 April 2020) was a French professional [[association football|footballer]] who played as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]].\n\n==Career==\nBorn in [[Paris]], Bernard played club football for [[Paris-Neuilly]], [[Stade Rennais F.C.|Rennes]], [[Paris Saint-Germain F.C.|Paris Saint-Germain]], [[Stade Brestois 29|Brest]] and [[AS Monaco FC|Monaco]].<ref name=\"auto\"/>\n\nHe represented France at youth level, but never played for the senior team, though he was an unused substitute on one occasion.<ref name=\"auto1\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.ouest-france.fr/bretagne/brest-29200/stade-brestois-deces-de-l-ancien-gardien-de-daniel-bernard-6804166|title=Football. D\u00e9c\u00e8s de Daniel Bernard, l\u2019ancien gardien de but de Brest et Rennes|date=9 April 2020|website=Ouest-France.fr}}</ref>\n\n==Later life and death==\nBernard died on 9 April 2020 aged 70, a few weeks after the death of his daughter.<ref name=\"auto1\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bernard, Daniel}}\n[[Category:1949 births]]\n[[Category:2020 deaths]]\n[[Category:French footballers]]\n[[Category:Stade Rennais F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Paris Saint-Germain F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Stade Brestois 29 players]]\n[[Category:AS Monaco FC players]]\n[[Category:Ligue 2 players]]\n[[Category:Ligue 1 players]]\n[[Category:Association football goalkeepers]]\n[[Category:France youth international footballers]]\n\n{{France-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|French footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name           = Daniel Bernard\n|image          = \n|image_size     = \n|caption        = \n|fullname       = \n|birth_date     = {{birth date|1949|9|29|df=y}}\n|birth_place    = [[Paris]], France\n|death_date     = {{death date and age|2020|4|9|1949|9|29|df=y}}\n|death_place    = \n|height         = 1.77m<ref name=\"auto\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.footballdatabase.eu/fr/joueur/details/45852|title=Daniel Bernard - Stats - palmar\u00e8s|website=www.footballdatabase.eu}}</ref>\n|position       = [[Goalkeeper (association football)|Goalkeeper]]\n|youthyears1    = \n|youthclubs1    = \n|years1         = 1968\u20131969\n|clubs1         = [[Paris-Neuilly]]\n|caps1          = 25\n|goals1         = 0\n|years2         = 1969\u20131977\n|clubs2         = [[Stade Rennais F.C.|Rennes]]\n|caps2          = 152\n|goals2         = 0\n|years3         = 1977\u20131978\n|clubs3         = [[Paris Saint-Germain F.C.|Paris Saint-Germain]]\n|caps3          = 29\n|goals3         = 0\n|years4         = 1978\u20131984\n|clubs4         = [[Stade Brestois 29|Brest]]\n|caps4          = 188\n|goals4         = 0\n|years5         = 1984\u20131985\n|clubs5         = [[AS Monaco FC|Monaco]]\n|caps5          = 13\n|goals5         = 0\n|totalcaps      = 407\n|totalgoals     = 0\n|nationalyears1 = \n|nationalteam1  = France youth\n|nationalcaps1  = \n|nationalgoals1 = \n}}\n'''Daniel Bernard''' (29 September 1949 \u2013 9 April 2020) was a French professional [[association football|footballer]] who played as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]].\n\n==Career==\nBorn in [[Paris]], Bernard played club football for [[Paris-Neuilly]], [[Stade Rennais F.C.|Rennes]], [[Paris Saint-Germain F.C.|Paris Saint-Germain]], [[Stade Brestois 29|Brest]] and [[AS Monaco FC|Monaco]].<ref name=\"auto\"/>\n\nHe represented France at youth level, but never played for the senior team, though he was an unused substitute on one occasion.<ref name=\"auto1\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.ouest-france.fr/bretagne/brest-29200/stade-brestois-deces-de-l-ancien-gardien-de-daniel-bernard-6804166|title=Football. D\u00e9c\u00e8s de Daniel Bernard, l\u2019ancien gardien de but de Brest et Rennes|date=April 9, 2020|website=Ouest-France.fr}}</ref>\n\n==Later life and death==\nBernard died on 9 April 2020 aged 70, a few weeks after the death of his daughter.<ref name=\"auto1\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bernard, Daniel}}\n[[Category:1949 births]]\n[[Category:2020 deaths]]\n[[Category:French footballers]]\n[[Category:Stade Rennais F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Paris Saint-Germain F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Stade Brestois 29 players]]\n[[Category:AS Monaco FC players]]\n[[Category:Ligue 2 players]]\n[[Category:Ligue 1 players]]\n[[Category:Association football goalkeepers]]\n[[Category:France youth international footballers]]\n\n{{France-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "GiantSnowman", "label": "safe", "comment": "date formats perMOS:DATEFORMATbyscript", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel_Bernard_(footballer)"}
